Package smarthome.persistence.mem

Class HouseRepositoryMemImpl

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.mem.HouseRepositoryMemImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<HouseName, House>, IHouseRepository
public class HouseRepositoryMemImpl extends Object implements IHouseRepository
Repository class for managing the persistence and retrieval of House instances.

This repository is backed by an in-memory HashMap data structure. It is an in-memory implementation of the repository. The repository is responsible for managing the storage and retrieval of House instances.
